              "title": "Practice — useState & useEffect Hooks",
              "instructions": "Fetch students from Spring Boot API. Show loading spinner, error state. Filter by dept (useState). Auto-refresh every 30 sec.",
              "hint": "useEffect cleanup: return () => clearInterval(timerId) to stop auto-refresh on unmount."
